msgstr "规则可以与以下动作之一关联。当数据包与规则的选择条件匹配时，将执行指定的动作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/firewalls/_index.adoc:1199
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`allow | accept | pass | permit`: these keywords are equivalent and allow "
